---
title: Filaments
permalink: /filaments/index.html
---

<p>A running catalog of the 3D printing filaments I keep on hand, grouped by type. Spool weights are the amount left on the active spool; spares are sealed rolls in the closet.</p>

<div class="container card-container">
  {%- if catalog.filaments.lowStock.length > 0 %}
    <div class="center-heading"><h2>Low Stock</h2></div>
    <div class="row">
      {%- for filament in catalog.filaments.lowStock %}
        {% include "filamentitem.njk" %}
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
    <hr/>
  {%- endif %}
  {%- for group in catalog.filaments.byMaterial %}
    <div class="center-heading"><h2>{{ group.material }}</h2></div>
    <div class="row">
      {%- for filament in group.filaments %}
        {% include "filamentitem.njk" %}
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
    {%- if not loop.last %}<hr/>{% endif %}
  {%- endfor %}
</div>
